{"tid":2078364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿聯酋航班26人確診 何栢良︰讓同機客留禁區屬漏洞","createTime":"2020-06-25T03:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T03:59:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"118c0c87ebebb8c94a0fb22c09e721c0a20128a0","tid":2078364,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"阿聯酋航班26人確診 何栢良︰讓同機客留禁區屬漏洞<br />\n2020-06-25 HKT 10:55<br />\n<br />\n11名內地人由迪拜坐飛機抵達香港，原本打算轉機返回內地，但由於沒有目的地的登機證，在本港機場滯留5天，同機有26多名乘客先後確診新型肺炎。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，機上有多人確診，同機乘客應被視為緊密接觸者，任由他們滯留機場禁區是防疫的漏洞，政府部門有需要檢討。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534039-20200625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534039-20200625.htm&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=fa8da06a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534039-20200625.htm&h=c906c011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534039-20200625.htm</a>"}]}